==Trivia==
*In the comics, Jennifer Kale is the cousin of [[Johnny Blaze]] and Danny Ketch, as well as a sorcerer apprentice of Dakimh the Enchanter, who served as an ally of [[Man-Thing]]. Kale was killed by [[Victoria Hand]] under [[Daniel Drumm]]'s influence, and later resurrected, assisting [[Maria Hill]] and [[Elektra]] against [[Bullseye]] and the [[Hand]].
*Kale's outfit features many symbols symbolizing her journey, including an icon of two hands being bound.{{Ref|TMoAAA}}

==Behind the Scenes==
*[[Ivy Haralson]], [[Jemini Powell]], [[Annelisa Richards]] and [[Shara London]] were stunt doubles for [[Sasheer Zamata]] in the role of Jennifer Kale.

